data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This exquisite, custom-built luxury home boasts 5 BR's (potentially 7), 4 Full Baths, and a fully finished walkout basement, unparalleled living experience in a desirable cul-de-sac location. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the grandeur of vaulted ceilings, emanating an air of sophistication and warmth. The open living area is enveloped w/ natural light, highlighting the stone fireplace & elegant hardwood flooring, and accentuating the impeccable attention to detail throughout. This gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, complete with built in dbl ovens, gas range and accented hood, custom cabinetry, expansive island, granite countertops, and breakfast area, all perfect for culinary endeavors or family entertaining. Nestled just behind the kitchen you'll discover the laundry room w/ utility sink, a Full Bath, and a BR or office. The luxury continues into the main floor spacious Primary suite, custom walk-on closet, then seamlessly flow through to the Primary Bath centered by a clawfoot soaking tub, radial recessed ceiling and chandelier, dual flanked vanities, and walk-in shower, and a separate entrance from the BR to the deck overlooking the well-maintained lawn & spiral staircase to the lower patio. As you venture upstairs, you'll find a cozy family room centered around 2 additional spacious BR's, a Full Bath, and a converted grand dressing room. Escape to full-finished basement that presents endless opportunities for recreation and leisure, with an open Family Room w/ a modern electric fireplace, rec room w/ full decked out wet bar, home-gym room behind sliding doors, another large BR, luxury Full Bath w/ expanded walk-in shower operated by a tankless water heater, and a study with coffered ceiling. Retreat outside into the Hot Tub or sit by the wood-burning firepit or cook up a feast on the built-in kitchen area complete w/ a pellet grill. This exceptional home is a rare find. Don't miss the chance to make this extraordinary residence your own and schedule your private viewing today and prepare to be captivated by the allure of this remarkable home!
